OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe UK theatre industry is "under
OL,8,Fgrowing pressure" due to rising
OL,9,Fproduction costs and is in need of
OL,10,Fpolicy reforms as the demand for live
OL,11,Fperformance continues to soar, a
OL,12,Freport has said.
OL,14,FThe costs of running and creating
OL,15,Ftheatre continues to pose a threat to
OL,16,Fthe industry with policy changes
OL,17,Fneeded to help "stabilise the sector
OL,18,Fand unlock growth", according to a
OL,19,Freport from the Society of London
OL,20,FTheatre (SOLT) and UK Theatre.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@QO]yD@POUzD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
