OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe report, which examined the state
OL,8,Fof theatre in the UK in 2026, said:
OL,9,F"While demand for live performance has
OL,10,Fnever been higher, the financial model
OL,11,Fbehind producing theatre is under
OL,12,Fgrowing pressure."
OL,14,FIt added: "Production budgets have
OL,15,Fclimbed steadily over the past decade
OL,16,Fas labour, materials, energy and
OL,17,Fbuilding maintenance costs have
OL,18,Fincreased.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@RO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"At the same time, theatres have
OL,8,Flargely held ticket prices steady in
OL,9,Freal terms to protect access for
OL,10,Faudiences."
OL,12,FThe report found that UK theatres are
OL,13,F"busier than ever" with more than 37
OL,14,Fmillion people attending across the UK
OL,15,Flast year, with London's West End
OL,16,Faccounting for 17 million.
OL,18,FIt also estimated that the average
OL,19,Fprice of a West End ticket is 8.9%
OL,20,Flower in real terms than in 2019, with
OL,21,Fless than 4% of tickets exceeding #150.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]uD@AOUuD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe report projects that 91% of
OL,8,Ftheatres expect total costs to rise,
OL,9,Fincluding staffing, supply, energy and
OL,10,Fbuilding maintenance.
OL,12,FIt outlined policy changes that could
OL,13,Fhelp the sector's financial
OL,14,Fsustainability, such as reforming
OL,15,Fbusiness rates for theatres, extending
OL,16,Ftheatre tax relief to support touring
OL,17,Fproductions, introducing stronger
OL,18,Fincentives for donations, and ensuring
OL,19,Fpublic funding settlements keep pace
OL,20,Fwith inflation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"With the right policy environment,
OL,8,Ftheatre can continue to grow as one of
OL,9,Fthe UK's most distinctive cultural and
OL,10,Feconomic strengths," it said.
OL,12,FThe report added that despite the
OL,13,Fsoaring popularity of live
OL,14,Fperformance, 36% of theatres will face
OL,15,Fan operating deficit in 2026, rising
OL,16,Fto 51% in the subsidised sector.
OL,18,FIt also found that 36% of UK theatres
OL,19,Fexpect turnover to increase this year,
OL,20,Fdown from 60% last year.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
