PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe SOLT and UK Theatre described the
OL,8,Fsuggested interventions as
OL,9,F"investments in a sector that already
OL,10,Fdelivers substantial economic and
OL,11,Fsocial returns", and highlighted how
OL,12,Fthe theatre sector supports creative
OL,13,Fjobs, attracts international visitors
OL,14,Fand drives local economic activity.
OL,16,FThe report said: "Theatres do not just
OL,17,Fprovide entertainment. They train the
OL,18,Fwriters, directors, designers and
OL,19,Fperformers who power the wider
OL,20,Fcreative industries.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@OO]xD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
