PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"They also act as civic anchors in
OL,8,Fcommunities across the country,
OL,9,Fsustaining local high streets,
OL,10,Fsupporting thousands of jobs, and
OL,11,Fproviding education and community
OL,12,Fprogrammes that reach young people and
OL,13,Ffamilies every day."
OL,15,FSOLT and UK Theatre co-chief
OL,16,Fexecutives Claire Walker and Hannah
OL,17,FEssex said: "Theatres across the UK
OL,18,Fare entertaining millions of people
OL,19,Fand producing work that inspires
OL,20,Faudiences around the world.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@TO]yD@MOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
