PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Every day our members are also
OL,8,Frunning education programmes,
OL,9,Fsupporting young people, and bringing
OL,10,Fcommunities together through live
OL,11,Fperformance.
OL,13,F"The public appetite for theatre is
OL,14,Fclear. But the organisations that make
OL,15,Fit possible are facing rising costs on
OL,16,Falmost every front.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
