CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773411077
OL,3,CUK theatre 'under growing pressure'
OL,4,Cfrom rising production costs, report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"The challenge now is ensuring this
OL,8,Fsuccess is sustainable, so theatres
OL,9,Facross the country can continue
OL,10,Fcreating new work, supporting jobs and
OL,11,Freaching audiences everywhere."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@_O]
